      • disableNativeComponentsInOnlineSigning

        public void disableNativeComponentsInOnlineSigning(android.content.Context context,
                                                   boolean disable)

        Allows Online Signing to load in complete non-native manner. This results in hiding actionbar & bottom toolbar, uses online signature adoption component and disables other native SDK UI components.

        Parameters:
        context - Application Context
        disable - if true, then native SDK components for Online Signing will be disabled. Default value is false

      • isNativeComponentsInOnlineSigningDisabled
